 <span data-ttu-id="bd040-154">Il <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedAudio.WriteToAudioStream%2A> metodo Usa lo stesso formato binario, ma non include l'intestazione di Wave.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bd040-154">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedAudio.WriteToAudioStream%2A> method uses the same binary format, but does not include the Wave header.</span></span>  
  
   
  
